    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: April 5, 2026</p>

    <p>These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your access to and use of the Fund-Raise platform (the "Service") provided by Fund-Raise ("we," "our," or "us"). By accessing or using the Service, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the Service.</p>

    <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>By creating an account, signing in, or otherwise using the Service, you represent that you are at least 18 years old and have the authority to enter into these Terms on behalf of yourself or the organization you represent. If you are using the Service on behalf of an organization, you agree to these Terms on behalf of that organization and represent that you have the authority to do so.</p>

    <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
    <p>Fund-Raise is a fundraising intelligence platform designed for foundations and nonprofit organizations. The Service enables users to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Upload and process fundraising data via Excel/CSV files or CRM integrations</li>
        <li>View real-time dashboards, KPI tracking, and performance metrics</li>
        <li>Analyze donor behavior using RFM scoring, segmentation, retention analytics, lifecycle tracking, and conversion metrics</li>
        <li>Identify at-risk donors through LYBUNT/SYBUNT analysis, upgrade/downgrade tracking, and recurring pattern detection</li>
        <li>Track fundraising goals by department and individual fundraiser</li>
        <li>Use AI-powered features including a natural language assistant, writing tools, anomaly detection, and smart recommendations</li>
        <li>Draft communications using AI writing tools for appeal letters, thank-you letters, impact stories, meeting prep, and weekly digests</li>
        <li>Compare campaigns, appeals, funds, and fiscal years side by side</li>
        <li>Collaborate through team tools including a message board, kudos wall, milestones, and fundraising bingo</li>
        <li>Connect to Blackbaud Raiser's Edge NXT for real-time CRM data access</li>
        <li>Configure organization settings including logo, mission statement, and branding</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Accounts and Access</h2>

