    <p>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your Google account used to access the Service. You must immediately notify us of any unauthorized access or security breach. We are not liable for any loss resulting from unauthorized use of your account.</p>

    <h3>3.3 Role-Based Access</h3>
    <p>The Service uses role-based access control with three levels: viewer, uploader, and admin. Your organization's administrator assigns roles and is responsible for ensuring appropriate access levels. Admin users have additional capabilities including organization profile management, CRM data import, integration configuration, and user management.</p>

    <h2>4. Acceptable Use</h2>
